{"id":"421466262d3c27341522606d3ec2423910c6ab763a10c022d2b8816b6dadf6f7","item_id":"200d95fc96:0","text":"定义空间与颜色中的 How 和 What"}
{"id":"9868b4e69fee4d43ba809f8f0fd2107478ddd89c5135fb7d9c7e2304cdd40887","item_id":"200d95fc96:1","text":"如果只是在 RenderMan 场景中加入一些灯光和对象，它确实能生成一张图像，但形状只是纯色，也只有建模时已有的细节。着色是一种细化并增强颜色与细节的方法，可以把泥塑般的模型转化为匹配甚至超越现实的图像。"}
{"id":"e587f4c737395660387ad3849be147df089c48d91c7306e3da7fc56b06e30b1d","item_id":"200d95fc96:2","text":"RenderMan 中的着色分为两个领域：空间与颜色。"}
{"id":"9d5a91862d8ca69c50a266a544b65c283a5f074baab113435f054d25ee10cc2b","item_id":"200d95fc96:3","text":"当 RenderMan 对 3D 对象进行着色时，置换着色让你有机会在空间中细化最终建模表面的位置。"}
{"id":"9c2a0e6adbb14d7ee7a50eca2c819fdb84f18a4ff23c8f3499d34a348ed70cf8","item_id":"200d95fc96:4","text":"随后，材质着色提供工具，用于细化对象与光的交互方式，从而定义它的颜色。"}
{"id":"2d3d46c363ef86482cc0fb70c575a3bf0ef6802541d9c5f7fac7c94b97c58894","item_id":"200d95fc96:5","text":"置换和材质着色通过互连节点组成的网络描述给渲染器，就像纹理连接到材质属性一样。"}
{"id":"d4ebf1ed154cdc2e45775ae52faa39d158bc82bc0ae270abfcfe7a945d527705","item_id":"200d95fc96:6","text":"在对象表面上变化的值称为着色信号，这些信号会沿着网络连接流动，并在网络节点中被创建、修改或混合。在 RenderMan 中，我们进一步把这些网络划分为定义表面"}
{"id":"7470bd3bc2abfe497af32ee4ccf845cb2aba14878d55c970d38d99629ab5d6a3","item_id":"200d95fc96:7","text":"How（如何）"}
{"id":"7470bd3bc2abfe497af32ee4ccf845cb2aba14878d55c970d38d99629ab5d6a3","item_id":"200d95fc96:15","text":"How（如何）"}
{"id":"44359e21492d788147966d8c0bc5beb2f4f4d0d05dd36f3ff36a0cd36a349907","item_id":"200d95fc96:8","text":"以及"}
{"id":"f8cf83a76a98df2dd4799b4d0d4f6ffc9af9a3a72d8648f94ca7cdea4b52fde7","item_id":"200d95fc96:9","text":"What（内容）"}
{"id":"f8cf83a76a98df2dd4799b4d0d4f6ffc9af9a3a72d8648f94ca7cdea4b52fde7","item_id":"200d95fc96:12","text":"What（内容）"}
{"id":"f95dff2a9d48de6cf2e8b0ab23c7d3f9890cc0d0ef8d787ef802c6085c82ed21","item_id":"200d95fc96:10","text":"的节点。"}
{"id":"fb72175906b755ae0320696c63963081aa69a886e96f8e87cb77a524de27d590","item_id":"200d95fc96:11","text":"网络的大部分由 Pattern 节点组成，这些节点描述"}
{"id":"9197d3f4571b40db28d74640af3d95070cca7db3e7786cb061cbbbdaad3c0586","item_id":"200d95fc96:13","text":"；它们帮助着色艺术家精确控制表面上每一点的信号值。"}
{"id":"7e7e9dff10b8b5bf5409cc4c3d1f5b04cdf56b25838e69eeeeac1b665a70805a","item_id":"200d95fc96:14","text":"在网络的最末端，着色信号会被送入 Displace 或 Bxdf（材质）节点，这些节点定义"}
{"id":"f3e04ced5a9f2b22b4cda681f0280e06128b0a874660cf93f42d311edb6e1f4f","item_id":"200d95fc96:16","text":"；它们高度依赖数学和物理，用来定义表面位置被改变的空间，以及表面与光交互时所使用的精确模型。"}
{"id":"94fe01d8a4364a96a1e22216d837470ca7e110ca02a2503238240f81819a2f7f","item_id":"200d95fc96:17","text":"主要着色工作流是使用这些节点库，以不同方式把它们连接起来，并调整它们的各种控制项，以获得想要的外观。"}
{"id":"de07913c2d706107c909c8aa8b94162c5994be040a1893af2a16792d4fe1f08c","item_id":"200d95fc96:18","text":"RenderMan 提供一组核心 Displace 和 Bxdf 节点，它们代表了真实感表面模型的最新成果，同时还提供一套 Pattern 节点库，可组合起来复现极其复杂的表面外观。"}
{"id":"9e80040275685266e3c5be0db33ee88bc75962ac1bccac2399311c74f577c9ee","item_id":"200d95fc96:19","text":"对于高级用户，有多种选项可以从头创建自己的节点；这些主题不在此处介绍，而可以在我们的"}
{"id":"3fb7b39416f1d067268747fc214494d759d2609f863ace1a8a76705618d5c80b","item_id":"200d95fc96:20","text":"开发者"}
{"id":"894e988cdf94caa95b745c4df2c1f2a90ce5738b56aac00c997080d2c90d7fba","item_id":"200d95fc96:21","text":"文档中找到。"}
{"id":"f348fb4839ffa800f075c903cd2a24cb79a3a0de3380fde5c8bb05ce5d5f29de","item_id":"200d95fc96:22","text":"置换"}
{"id":"92b507c6856096f1c2670267f1febc291fc82014b914fa3ede86ca801fbba23d","item_id":"200d95fc96:23","text":"置换着色器允许你在渲染时修改几何体，从而有效改变它的形状。"}
{"id":"2b1495fd56193247d79ded5e78addae0c34f0221782693ccbbebba6aacb9fef5","item_id":"200d95fc96:24","text":"这样可以添加比原始建模更多的细节。"}
{"id":"e3bc727513d7a3e1169f749e1ac20ca42e4c53a397f053fea13e6c316a345103","item_id":"200d95fc96:25","text":"通常，来自雕刻工具的精细细节正是在这里实际应用到模型上的。做法是从原始模型获取表面信息，并逐点移动表面。Displace 着色器是唯一能执行这种修改的对象，但可以通过 Pattern 节点网络或从雕刻软件导出的纹理，告诉它修改多少以及沿哪些方向修改。"}
{"id":"fd10a146e9625bfd3f69639eeb5fbee0eae7e4633222f1ee3d3d36395844303e","item_id":"200d95fc96:26","text":"材质"}
{"id":"c526885593bfd2479e93b156b6cbfd499d79ac815ae1ecd4a244912247a13f6e","item_id":"200d95fc96:27","text":"RenderMan 中的材质通常称为 Bxdf。Bxdf 会把材质描述给"}
{"id":"168196d133817ed25c3fe0bf9a5254309ab899daa622e81d3ead0daf0eb33def","item_id":"200d95fc96:28","text":"积分器"}
{"id":"9bca274ac08027940d612824c6cf7250419df4e852e9fad358db53be0be6a4b6","item_id":"200d95fc96:29","text":"，由积分器决定最终渲染外观。"}
{"id":"59208cd6b6d765c3b4c044200d99c7d42998f6fb43c05a3f025d6cdac8e9bab8","item_id":"200d95fc96:30","text":"由于二者彼此独立，用户可以更换积分器，同时仍然使用同一个 Bxdf 来获得一致或符合预期的结果。"}
{"id":"62de0345912960161b9e79e268ad7f2673c02110bfae080ca28ba447291fe0d9","item_id":"200d95fc96:31","text":"假设你创建了一种金色金属材质，如果用 PxrPathTracer 或 PxrVCM 渲染它，你会期望最终图像中的材质属性仍然被看作“金”。这甚至可以扩展到非照片写实和自定义积分器：它们会以新的、有趣的方式渲染你的金色 Bxdf，但结果仍会被理解为金色（或金色质感）。"}
{"id":"1fdc430004cf3d8e3209b41ea98aedfdeb5170ed67845f1a2a177bfa5465d195","item_id":"200d95fc96:32","text":"这就是 RenderMan 中材质 Bxdfs 的强大之处。"}
{"id":"ac28c531421f2d044d172e7fd699dceb991d423da9731101a5c331de95f51b7b","item_id":"200d95fc96:33","text":"下面按常见用途列出 RenderMan 中可用材质的链接。"}
{"id":"14bc49591628685b3e38a7eb303e058f43d5cc342f0739aec31bbc30250fb5ef","item_id":"200d95fc96:34","text":"PxrSurface 和 Layering"}
{"id":"ebe46811da2358beaedf1a7442f06c90316cc30c85460c1d18a970711da706eb","item_id":"200d95fc96:35","text":"- 这是用于创建几乎所有所需外观的终极材质系统。从皮肤到宝石，PxrSurface 都能通过分层和艺术家驱动的参数处理复杂外观。"}
{"id":"34797d5e8cfbab69b5286c487856969d7a4c8936127fe0ce02d29e03966258fc","item_id":"200d95fc96:36","text":"MaterialX Lama - Layered Materials"}
{"id":"1a6dd548a8a2aafac9df38dc25c3a8801ca269490dd2f188e65c428dae474760","item_id":"200d95fc96:37","text":"- 由 Industrial Light & Magic 开发的材质分层系统。"}
{"id":"6b2b3cbd4ad476016050e61b781d1112117b06945fb578fbffcfc4ff3f6daa69","item_id":"200d95fc96:38","text":"PxrVolume"}
{"id":"03380220a988aa802f37a7f21ac64be8b5496728f1dbb239e265effbcfe6b6a6","item_id":"200d95fc96:39","text":"- 一种强大而快速的体积着色器，用于烟、火、爆炸等效果。"}
{"id":"ccf31fc48275c143b867da4b33a4ee3f6d4e505c6b15e85616384686e98b23fe","item_id":"200d95fc96:40","text":"PxrMarschnerHair"}
{"id":"f362e0e87c7b09d58543a200a9c9c4ddf6432f87593b54e5dacdd29c1a3d7618","item_id":"200d95fc96:41","text":"- 这种材质专为头发、毛发和纤维设计。"}
{"id":"f380d30f8481b984621452835584792ce119bc8c4fd19bc2bff61812052f6f83","item_id":"200d95fc96:42","text":"基础材质"}
{"id":"b2796e3f880ca72d3907b2b74e45a81e18509f6eb7d8f8971cbc1a3b959439f9","item_id":"200d95fc96:43","text":" - 这些材质是为特定用途设计的。"}
{"id":"20f53349b9fef849eb5e27f738ed21d56ab95a3635ae66bd3c0a614058279948","item_id":"200d95fc96:44","text":"PxrConstant"}
{"id":"bffd31a1071728d658cf0fb6890da0401a71478ac2c45233936ee2b0ec4d0240","item_id":"200d95fc96:45","text":"- 这种材质提供恒定颜色，也可以连接纹理。它非常适合投射以及其他不希望产生着色的效果。"}
{"id":"989730b0317d6d4e5c702f6ba2ef05b9b93f02c3c3ef1eba4d57eb929ea2df03","item_id":"200d95fc96:46","text":"PxrDiffuse"}
{"id":"171524ae3b553c9aa657ee9fa299fef495f002da3f740976f50b8fae3d102420","item_id":"200d95fc96:47","text":" - 一种简单快速的漫反射材质。"}
{"id":"ca6e9359019eea08d170f12ef85506fb6ede83064a7deed0382b113f737f6a97","item_id":"200d95fc96:48","text":"PxrBlack"}
{"id":"250eb2c542517f9b9ad24ee1236cb1847b7a93ce4d59f54102a40011c8194eb0","item_id":"200d95fc96:49","text":" - 一种不散射材质，渲染结果就如其名：黑色。"}
{"id":"160a13d94fb047389d47be363a4de1af8d6f8d2024d1e8c70a62e41ff072669d","item_id":"200d95fc96:50","text":"图案"}
{"id":"160a13d94fb047389d47be363a4de1af8d6f8d2024d1e8c70a62e41ff072669d","item_id":"200d95fc96:51","text":"图案"}
{"id":"c45f24712a601d295d8d26e2bd82a3ce47df26acc934a1356d18de1e61cbddc2","item_id":"200d95fc96:52","text":"也可用于改变材质的着色。"}
{"id":"1c77415d880e37e8b28e6b8dc7560b5c84f15dac25d5a36f72eaca83a90658bf","item_id":"200d95fc96:53","text":"它们可以直接改变结果（例如你想要一个"}
{"id":"0e38d6cf32e83e7d17dd744f1b68590375c6bb973efc32f08661f40599a93069","item_id":"200d95fc96:54","text":"棋盘格"}
{"id":"9cb1210a07aeba467cbdb2b4df53d5037a8a641a1adffaa0d3e79564fb252507","item_id":"200d95fc96:55","text":"地板），也可以用于驱动其他参数，比如使用 PxrFlakes 创建金属漆！"}
{"id":"9318803981dc8e7a80c83967d51fb55151c2fefe23b771cb62edf38979e6aa75","item_id":"200d95fc96:56","text":"RenderMan 附带了大量图案和实用工具，可组合成有用的外观。"}
